[package]
name = "gnome-app-utils"
description = "Utilities for my Gnome apps"
homepage = "https://codeberg.org/swsnr/gnome-app-utils.rs"
repository = "https://codeberg.org/swsnr/gnome-app-utils.rs"
license = "EUPL-1.2"
authors = [ "Sebastian Wiesner <sebastian@swsnr.de>",]
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2024"
publish = false
rust-version = "1.89"

[dependencies]
futures = "0.3.31"
libc = "0.2.174"
log = "0.4.27"

[dependencies.gdk4-wayland]
version = "0.10.0"
features = [ "v4_18",]

[dependencies.gdk4-x11]
version = "0.10.0"
features = [ "v4_18",]

[dependencies.gio]
version = "0.21.1"
features = [ "v2_84",]

[dependencies.glib]
version = "0.21.1"
features = [ "log", "v2_84",]

[dependencies.gtk]
package = "gtk4"
version = "0.10.0"
features = [ "gnome_48",]

[dependencies.strum]
version = "0.27.1"
features = [ "derive",]
